Package: pan.corpus.generator
Title: Pulls PAN-AV Data into R and Creates Corpus Object
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ben", "Cross", , "ben.cross@postgrad.manchester.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5430-1659"))
Description: This package is used to pull the various styles of PAN-AV corpus into R and to create a combined corpus object if required. The PAN-AV datasets are used as benchmarking datasets in the field of Authorship Verification.
